Implemented the featured-paper change end to end.

`featured_paper` is now an explicit nullable field in [schemas/digest.json](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/schemas/digest.json), emitted by [src/eegfm_digest/render.py](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/src/eegfm_digest/render.py) and passed through [src/eegfm_digest/pipeline.py](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/src/eegfm_digest/pipeline.py). The CLI now supports `--feature-paper` in [src/eegfm_digest/run.py](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/src/eegfm_digest/run.py), and that is the only remaining path that sets a featured paper. I removed the old auto-pick behavior from the site payload/manifest flow in [src/eegfm_digest/site.py](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/src/eegfm_digest/site.py) and the browser fallback logic in [docs/assets/site.js](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/docs/assets/site.js), so GitHub Actions won’t auto-set one anymore unless someone explicitly passes the flag.

For rendering, the month page now has a dedicated featured slot, and when `featured_paper` is explicitly `null` it shows the muted dashed card you asked for. The styles live in [docs/assets/style.css](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/docs/assets/style.css). I also updated [SPEC.md](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/SPEC.md) to match the new digest/CLI contract.

Tests added/updated:
- [tests/test_search_e2e.py](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/tests/test_search_e2e.py): browser-level null-featured render check
- [tests/test_pipeline_outputs.py](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/tests/test_pipeline_outputs.py): digest default `null` and explicit `--feature-paper` persistence
- [tests/test_architecture_stability.py](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/tests/test_architecture_stability.py): CLI flag wiring and invalid featured id rejection
- [tests/test_render_site.py](/Users/ismaelrobles-razzaq/2_cs_projects/EEG-FM-Digest/tests/test_render_site.py): payload/snapshot updates

